settings.description: After a "long" adventure, you finally made it! Now you must go through the entire world to get to the final boss, bowser. Take the Hammer suit with you and a few more powerups to defeat him!
A short level that shows Mario saving all the dimensions from destruction.

This level has 5 ace coins, so you need to recollect it,
Infact, this is my nice level ever made, you need a hammer to destroy it by getting the 3-ups in a giant question mark block.
Bowser's secret airship, so Mario can head to Luigi's castle undetected.
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is the bunker part; you will see this again soon.
Magic Blocks, are on Buster Beetle Room, also Room 4 is Bonus Room, so Enjoy!
Use the metal mushroom to get to the top of the temple, where you'll face off against Big Boo!
Mario got lost in the desert, meanwhile he finds several pipes that direct him to different places but he wants to cross the barrier once and for all.

Fly, slide and spin through the sky and Bowser's castle!
(For Smaghetti Build Contest #2.)
